This product is a substantially rewritten fork of milla-jovovich/mempalace
(MIT license, Copyright 2025 MemPalace Contributors). The fork replaces
the storage backend (ChromaDB -> LanceDB), adds language-aware code mining,
incremental re-mining, export/import, code search, and 400+ tests.

